ygData.messageBody:
Hey Mel!


This is Fentus, I think you know me from the guild? If you didint get your
info for those spells, i did look them up ()sorry about the delay) the aura
one you need to get in the overthere, the earth one you need to reserach,
and the vision one you need to buy at any vendor. Sorry i dont remeber the
names of the spells but i'm asure you will get them. also are you on the
guild mailinf list? This mailing list is for glbts eq'rs in general and we
also have a list for the guild. If you did not recieve any info about that
when you joined, and you should have, please send an e-mail to
andy@... who is the guildleader. Additionally, I see you have a
warrior in my lvl range. UMMM I AM A WIZARD I NEED A TANK :) You would
be a great asset to us in the 30's range cuz all we have for a tank is my
scrawny ranger boyfriend :) So bring her on !!!!

-joe
Fentus
